quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  45,22,"And Allah created the skies and the earth in reality, so that every soul may be rewarded for that which it earned and (that) they may not be dealt with unjustly"
  45,23,"Then have you seen him who takes his desire for his god while Allah has left him to stray on (the basis of his) knowledge, and has set a seal on his hearing and his heart and has placed a covering on his sight? So who can guide him after Allah? Will you not then be mindful"
  45,24,"And they say, “There is nothing but our life of this world, we die and we live and nothing destroys us but time,” and they have no knowledge of that, they do nothing but guess"
  45,25,"And when Our clear signs are recited to them, their argument is nothing but that they say, “Bring (back) our fathers, if you are the truthful ones.” are the truthful ones.”"
  45,26,"Say, “Allah gives you life then He causes you to die, then He will gather you towards the day of resurrection, about which there is no doubt, but the majority of human beings does not know.”"